      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of every little detail, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really won't find another one this clean! Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude0a",
