    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 that serves as a benchmark for the S54 platform. This specimen features the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a double VANOS system that operates with surgical precision. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate, showing no signs of rear subframe fatigue, and retains its original suspension geometry and bushing compliance. Finished in collector-grade paint with a pristine cabin, this vehicle has been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy, ensuring all mechanical tolerances meet factory specifications. A transparent, high-performance investment for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
