      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector's specimen. The original deep-gloss paint remains flawless, protected by a professional ceramic coating, and is entirely free of stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its 'new car' aroma, featuring supple, unworn leather and pristine controls that show zero signs of use. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from a new vehicle, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained exclusively by the dealership with a full, documented service history. Every button, seal, and component functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a masterfully preserved example of automotive excellence that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
